        conseils: "If heading to Marseille-Provence Airport, specify this when booking as the airport rate may be more advantageous. Vitrolles is ideal as a base if you have an early morning flight: several budget hotels are located 3 km from the airport. The Rocher de Vitrolles is worth climbing (15 min walk from the car park): the 360° view is spectacular. The old village is charming for lunch (Le Rocher restaurant). Grand Vitrolles shopping centre is the largest in the department. Avoid departures between 5pm and 7pm on weekdays: the A7 between Marseille and Vitrolles is saturated at office closing times.",
